document.full_text: at least 15 people were killed by booby-traps and in ambushes set up by gaddafi brigades on saturday while withdrawing from the libyan city of misrata, a rebel spokesman told al jazeera television.
document.title: fifteen dead in gaddafi ambushes - rebel spokesman
